<item>
            <title>[CAMEL-17599] camel-jdbc - JdbcProducer leaks PreparedStatement</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-17599</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Originally reported on the a Quarkus Zulip thread:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/187030-users/topic/Camel.20JDBC.20leaks.20statement&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://quarkusio.zulipchat.com/#narrow/stream/187030-users/topic/Camel.20JDBC.20leaks.20statement&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There are 2 different execution paths in JdbcProducer. doCreateAndExecuteSqlStatementWithHeaders &amp;amp; doCreateAndExecuteSqlStatement.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;doCreateAndExecuteSqlStatementWithHeaders does close the PreparedStatement:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-3.14.1/components/camel-jdbc/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/jdbc/JdbcProducer.java#L185-L188&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-3.14.1/components/camel-jdbc/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/jdbc/JdbcProducer.java#L185-L188&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;doCreateAndExecuteSqlStatement does not:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-3.14.1/components/camel-jdbc/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/jdbc/JdbcProducer.java#L244-L246&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/blob/camel-3.14.1/components/camel-jdbc/src/main/java/org/apache/camel/component/jdbc/JdbcProducer.java#L244-L246&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This PR &amp;amp; commit suggests auto-closing is perhaps not desirable:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/6192&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/camel/pull/6192&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The code prior to Camel 3.12.x did close the PreparedStatement in the finally block, so maybe that should be restored.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
